title: NBA vs NFL Free Agency; Mailbag
itunes:title: NBA vs NFL Free Agency; Mailbag
description:
A conference room filled with two heroes- Dan Hanzus and Chris Wesseling bring you all of the latest news around the NFL including Cowboys star Ezekiel Elliot not facing suspension (10:28), Dolphins DT Kendrick Norton losing an arm in a car crash (12:11) and Gronk and Brady working out together (16:40). Would you ever lick ice cream to impress someone? (24:40) The heroes close out the show with a very important softball update with the two most important players on the team and THE mailbag. (30:25)
